Package com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.location

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.location.Location
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BillTo, ShipTo
    public abstract class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    The Location class is an abstract class with data fields for address information and a list of employees at this location.
    Author:
    ArthurVargas
